title: Power Move: CLICK TO CALL Your Legislator to Protect SNAP, WIC, and Head Start. TAKE ACTION NOW
description:
# Power Move: CLICK TO CALL Your Legislator to Protect SNAP, WIC, and Head Start. TAKE ACTION NOW.

## üìû Congress is preparing budget cuts that threaten our communities. Use your power. Call now.

Proposed cuts to **SNAP**, **WIC**, and **Head Start** would devastate families‚Äîgutting food programs, maternal healthcare, and early childhood education.

These are survival programs. If we don‚Äôt act now, millions will lose access to care, nourishment, and the support they need to thrive.

This is your moment to use your voice‚Äîand your power.

---

## ‚úî What‚Äôs at Stake

- **SNAP** helps feed **38+ million people** every month  
  ‚û§ [USDA SNAP Overview](https://www.fns.usda.gov/snap/supplemental-nutrition-assistance-program)

- **WIC** provides nutrition and health care for **6.6 million women, infants, and children**  
  ‚û§ [USDA WIC Program](https://www.fns.usda.gov/wic)

- **Head Start** supports **over 1 million children** through meals, mental health, and early learning  
  ‚û§ [Head Start Facts](https://eclkc.ohs.acf.hhs.gov/about-us/article/head-start-program-facts)

---

## üì£ How to Take Action

‚úÖ **Step 1: Call your Representative and both U.S. Senators**

You have **three federal lawmakers**‚Äîyour House Representative and two Senators. Call all three.

Need to find them?

- üèõÔ∏è [Look up your Representative (House)](https://www.house.gov/representatives/find-your-representative)  
- üèõÔ∏è [Look up your Senators (Senate)](https://www.senate.gov/senators/senators-contact.htm)

‚úÖ **Step 2: Review the script below** or write your own message

‚úÖ **Step 3: Click the button on this page** to be auto-connected to their office  
(No phone number needed‚Äîwe‚Äôll dial for you.)

---

## ‚òéÔ∏è Sample Call Script

> Hi, my name is \_\_\_\_ and I‚Äôm a constituent from \_\_\_\_ (ZIP code).  
>
> I‚Äôm calling to urge you to **fully fund SNAP, WIC, and Head Start** in the federal budget.  
>
> - SNAP helps feed **38+ million people** each month  
> - WIC supports **6.6 million mothers and children** with nutrition and care  
> - Head Start provides early learning and support to **1+ million children**  
>
> These programs helped me [insert your personal story, or why this matters to your family, church, or community].  
>
> Please protect these programs. I‚Äôll be calling each week until I know they‚Äôre fully funded.  
>
> Thank you.

---

## üß≠ What Happens When You Call

You‚Äôll first reach a **real operator at the U.S. Capitol Switchboard**.

- Say: ‚ÄúConnect me to [Senator or Representative NAME]‚Äù  
- They‚Äôll transfer you directly to their D.C. office  
- If the line is busy or you get voicemail, **leave a message**‚Äîit still gets logged

Have your **ZIP code and story ready**‚Äîand don‚Äôt be afraid to speak from the heart.

---

## üîÅ Keep the Pressure On

‚úî Call every week until the vote is done  
‚úî Ask 3 friends to call too  
‚úî Flood their phone lines‚Äîthey can‚Äôt ignore us

Justice has a League. And you have the power to act.

description:
